title: Camille reveal

embed.description: WIP] Champion Reveal: Camille, the Steel Shadow Continue reading for more information! ""Precision is the difference between a butcher and a surgeon." Camille is an elite operative who works to maintain order for Piltover's established powers. It was her dedication to duty that led the Steel Shadow to transfigure her body into a hextech-powered death machine.
